---
// No se necesita JS
---
<section class="w-full py-20" id="rencauche">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      
      <!-- Image Column -->
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <img 
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-xl aspect-square shadow-xl" 
          alt="Technician inspecting the tread of a large tire in a workshop" 
          src="/images/retread.png"
          width="1000"
          height="1000"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Content Column -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 order-1 md:order-2">
        <div>
          <span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-2 block">Servicios Expertos</span>
          <h2 class="text-foreground text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black leading-tight mb-6">
            Segunda Vida para <br /> Tus Neumáticos
          </h2>
          <div class="h-1.5 w-20 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Nuestro proceso de rencauche certificado extiende la vida útil de sus equipos, ofreciendo un rendimiento comparable al de un neumático nuevo, pero a una fracción del costo.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface border border-border">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 p-2 rounded-full text-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">savings</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-foreground font-semibold">Ahorro de hasta 40% en costos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface border border-border">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 p-2 rounded-full text-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">eco</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-foreground font-semibold">Menor impacto ambiental</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface border border-border">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 p-2 rounded-full text-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified_user</span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-foreground font-semibold">Garantía total de operación</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>